\id PSA Drafted by Steven Dazim; edited by Steven Dazim; exeg checked by Marsha Miles, Francis Dagonov, Pais Ureka, David Berama; comprehension checked by many Aruamu folks in many different settings; PSA 1-50 cons ck by Jill Riepe in Aug 2014; PSA 51-99 cons ck by Norm Weatherhead in July 2014; PSA 100-118 cons ck by Norm Mundhenk in Sep 2012; PSA 119-150 by Norm Weatherhead in Apr 2013.
\h Onger Akaba
\toc3 OA
\toc2 Onger Akaba
\toc1 God…®n Ziam Fer Onger Akabar Ak…®nafarim
\mt1 God…®n Ziam Fer Onger Akabar Ak…®nafarim
\mt2 O
\mt1 Onger Akaba
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam, a Israelian Onger Akaba itir ak…®nafarim. Onger akar ak…®nafarir kam…®n itir maba, me Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n ikia God…®n D…®penim…®n da bange. Ez…® onger akar kabar maba, gumazamiziba uari os…®mt…®ziba ikia, God…®n ziam fer dughiam…®n dar gun m…®gei.
\ip En ganganim…®n, gumazir av…®riba ti onger akar kaba dughiar vam…®ran da osirizir puvat…®. Me dughiar igharaz igharazibar kamagh ami. Ez…® g…®n gumazir igharaziba da akuvagha ak…®nafarir vam…®ra gami.
\ip Onger akar kaba ko God ko m…®geir arazir kaba, dar n…®ghn…®zir av…®riba iti. Ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven akar kaba iti:
\ipi onger akar God…®n ziam feba,
\ipi ko uan arazir kuraba bagh God ko m…®k…®mt…® a da g…®n amangamin akaba,
\ipi ko os…®mt…®ziba ko m…®zaziba izir dughiam…®n, akurvazim bagha God ko m…®geir akaba,
\ipi ko atrivim am…®s…®vamimin dughiar ekiabar onger akaba,
\ipi ko n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n gun God…®n m…®k…®mamin ighiaba,
\ipi ko onger akar God m…®namamiba,
\ipi ko uan navir kuraba ko os…®mt…®ziba ag…®vs…® God ko m…®geir arazim,
\ipi ko God ko m…®k…®mt…® an apanibagh as…®ghas…®ghamin arazim,
\ipi ko onger akar gumazamiziba da baragh dar m…®g…®r…®g…®abar g…®n mangamiba.
\ip God ko m…®geir arazir kaba ko onger akar kaba, da gumazamiziba e itir ik…®r…®m…®rir kam bar ada avaragha dar gun m…®gei. En dughiar e bar akongeziba iti, en dughiar e os…®mt…®ziba isiba iti. En dughiar e igiabara itiba iti, en dughiar e ghuramiba iti. E dughiar mabar arei, egha dughiar mabar en naviba dera. Onger Akabar Ak…®nafarir kam, a ik…®r…®m…®rir e dat…®r…®gh…®n itir ikiamin dughiaba ko magh ghu, egha fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®k…®n onger akar kaba God…®n gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®ziba gavgavim dagh an…®ga, egha men ik…®r…®m…®rim…®n men akurvasi.
\c 1
\ms1 Ak…®nafarir namba 1\f + \fr 1:0 \ft Hibrun akam…®n aven, me Onger Akabar Ak…®nafarim…®n 5plan otevibagh ami, me dar bora ghaze, 5plan ak…®nafariba.\f*
